channel.description:
[center][b]I Getto I PK Video 3[/b]
Hey there! :)
This is my 3rd PK Video back in mid-late 2006.. When the Dds spec was changed.
A big thank you to http://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialNOG for featuring my videos <3 Please subscribe to them they will be posting more old videos. ;)
[youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nG4W7iIY3Zw[/youtube]
A few PK/Stake Screenshots from back in the day:
[img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/Part6.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/Part7.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/PK652.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/PK65M.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/PK422.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/PK164250K.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/PK207250K.jpg[/img] [img]http://i84.photobucket.com/albums/k11/I-Getto-I/Gettovsteletubbies.png[/img]

Thanks for watching.[/center]
